 2005</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"infobox-label\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; width=33%\">Venue</th><td class=\"infobox-data\">Tachi Palace Hotel &amp; Casino</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"infobox-label\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; width=33%\">City</th><td class=\"infobox-data\"><a href=\"/wiki/Lemoore,_California\" title=\"Lemoore, California\">Lemoore, California</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-header\" style=\"background:lightgrey;color:inherit; text-decoration:none;\">Event chronology</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-full-data\"><span></span>\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4em; vertical-align: top\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33%; text-align: center; padding: 0.2em 0.1em 0.2em 0\"><a href=\"/wiki/WEC_16\" title=\"WEC 16\">WEC 16: Clash of the Titans 2</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33%; text-align: center; padding: 0.2em 0.1em 0.2em 0.1em; font-weight: bold;\">WEC 17: Halloween Fury 4\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33%; text-align: center; padding: 0.2em 0 0.2em 0.1em\"><a href=\"/wiki/2006_in_WEC#WEC_18:_Unfinished_Business\" title=\"2006 in WEC\">WEC 18: Unfinished Business</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>WEC 17: Halloween Fury 4</b> was a <a href=\"/wiki/Mixed_martial_arts\" title=\"Mixed martial arts\">mixed martial arts</a> event promoted by <a href=\"/wiki/World_Extreme_Cagefighting\" title=\"World Extreme Cagefighting\">World Extreme Cagefighting</a> on October 14, 2005, at the Tachi Palace Hotel &amp; Casino in <a href=\"/wiki/Lemoore,_California\" title=\"Lemoore, California\">Lemoore, California</a>.<sup id=\"cite&#95;ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>1<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup> A light heavyweight tournament was held with the winner being crowned the champion and given a deal with the <a href=\"/wiki/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\" title=\"Ultimate Fighting Championship\">UFC</a>.<sup id=\"cite&#95;ref-WEC&#95;17&#95;2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-WEC_17-2\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>2<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</p>\n<meta property=\"mw:PageProp/toc\" />\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Results\">Results</h2><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=WEC_17&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Results\"><span>edit</span></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></div>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"font-size: 85%;\">\n\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"8\" style=\"background-color: #ccf; color: #000080; text-align: center;\">Main Card\n</th></tr>\n\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Weight class\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Method\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Round\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Time\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Light Heavyweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Scott_Smith_(fighter)\" title=\"Scott Smith (fighter)\">Scott Smith</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Tait Fletcher\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">TKO (Punches)\n</td>\n<td s